title: Naked Lunch
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Organic, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, English
description: A vegetarian food service located inside MOM's Organic Market. Offers fresh juices/smoothies, veggie burgers, bowls, and salads made with organic ingredients. Part of a chain located inside MOM's only. Make sure to mention that you want vegan bread if getting a sandwich. A new addition from the expansion recently opened in October 2015. Dine-in at the cafe with seating for around 12 or grab 'n go. May 2016 reported no longer fully vegan.
